Text: RE Follow upKevin I found out that we are not close at this point to a corp contract with Energy Central You would need to obtain a singe license user which is as follows Daliy Electric News Annually Daily Gas News Annually For Both Annually If you were to sign up this way and we did sign a corp contract Energy Central would credit you for the difference In the meantime in response to your question yes we can help you with this The best thing to do is go to at the top tool bar click on Request a Search Enter all of the detail you are looking for and your timeline and we will be able to fill your request If you have any questions please do not hesitate to call me Thank you Susan Original Message From Hyatt Kevin Sent Thursday July PM To Kennedy Susan L Subject RE Follow up Importance High In the meantime do you guys have access to any gas supply production forcasts for the Rockies and San Juan Basin areas Im looking into developing a new pipeline project and need to verify the gas supply will be there to fill the pipe Let me know thanks Kevin Hyatt x Original Message From Kennedy Susan L Sent Wednesday July PM To Hyatt Kevin Subject Follow up OLE Object Picture Metafile Kevin Just a follow up I have put in a request for your Dow Jones User Id and password I should have this by tomorrow I have left a message for Ben Smith at Energy Central and once I speak to him I will let you know If there is anything else in the mean time do not hesitate to call me Thank you Susan eSource Operations
